      <div class="tc-tag tag-client">Client Form</div>
      <div class="tc-name">Schedule a Delivery</div>
      <div class="tc-desc">Client-facing delivery request form. Submits directly to the monday Operations board in the Unconfirmed group.</div>
      <div class="tc-ftr"><span class="badge badge-live"><span class="badge-dot"></span>Live</span><div class="tc-arr"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#a0d6b4" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 17L17 7M7 7h10v10"/></svg></div></div>
